{"lastModified":1775746290618,"uri":"c::9938368400::vessel::d5cc4e96-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Balearic Islands\n\nLaunched in September 2020, luxurious Sunreef 60 sailing catamaran Calma offers 225m² of living space to enjoy life on board.\n\nCalma’s layout features five exclusive double ensuite cabins for ten guests, a stylish saloon with cosy lounging and dining areas, and a functional galley up, giving the chance to watch a professional chef in action.\n\nThanks to the sliding saloon door, the interior blends naturally with the outside, opening onto the large, sheltered aft deck and the splendid front terrace. The spacious flybridge features a BBQ, a wet bar and plenty of seating for enjoying the beautiful panoramic views.\n\nOperated by an experienced crew of 3, this grey-hulled beauty is available in the Balearics in summer.","blueprint":{"name":"CALMA","images":["/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cc4e96-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8d9e4c60-58d7-11f0-afb7-19b57e90b5c2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cc4e96-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae5ebfb0-3a38-11f0-b8be-adcef6fdd2fe/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cc4e96-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ae5e2370-3a38-11f0-b8be-adcef6fdd2fe/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cc4e96-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b46ce3a0-3a38-11f0-b8be-adcef6fdd2fe/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cc4e96-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b4413fc0-3a38-11f0-b8be-adcef6fdd2fe/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4e96-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7676-UMlu7z6tF.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4e96-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7676-xJR_xg627.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4e96-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-